                  "P-LI7"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Natural lithium foil (3.7 mg/cm2 thick)",
                "sandwiched between two Ta foils (3.9 mg/cm2 thick for",
                "front, 0.025 mm thick for back)."
              ]
            }
          ],
